Class InsightsViewController

java.lang.Object
no.ntnu.idatx1005.controller.BaseViewController
no.ntnu.idatx1005.controller.InsightsViewController
All Implemented Interfaces:
ButtonClickObserver, TaskEventObserver
public class InsightsViewController extends BaseViewController implements ButtonClickObserver

Insights View Controller

This class is responsible for handling the insights view. It extends the BaseViewController class and implements the ButtonClickObserver interface.

Since:
V1.1.0
Author:
William Holtsdalen
